@startuml EnZIM_System_Context
!theme plain
title EnZIM - System Context Diagram (C4 Level 1)
' Copyright (C) 2025 Robin L. M. Cheung, MBA. All rights reserved.

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Inter

actor "Student/Researcher\n(Offline Learner)" as student
actor "Traveler\n(On-the-go Reader)" as traveler
actor "Knowledge Explorer\n(Power User)" as explorer
actor "Archivist\n(Data Hoarder)" as archivist

rectangle "EnZIM System" as enzim #LightBlue {
    rectangle "EnZIM Application\n[Offline Knowledge Explorer]" as app
}

database "ZIM Archives\n[Wikipedia, Wikivoyage,\nWikibooks, etc.]" as zim #LightGreen
rectangle "AnZimmermanLib\n[Clean-Room ZIM Libraries]" as anzim #LightYellow
rectangle "Local AI Model\n[Optional LLM for\nQ&A Assistant]" as ai #LightPink
rectangle "OS TTS Engine\n[Text-to-Speech]" as tts #LightGray
rectangle "billedr\n[Entitlements Authority]" as billedr #LightGray

student --> app : Browse offline\nencyclopedias
traveler --> app : Read articles\non-the-go
explorer --> app : Explore semantic\nknowledge graph
archivist --> app : Manage large\narchive collections

app --> zim : Reads/writes
app --> anzim : Uses for ZIM\nparsing
app --> ai : Queries for\nQ&A/summaries
app --> tts : Reads articles\naloud
app --> billedr : Fetch signed\nentitlements

note right of enzim
  **EnZIM Vision**
  Offline-first knowledge companion
  combining high-fidelity ZIM reading
  with semantic navigation and
  AI-powered assistance.
  
  Proprietary Licensed (clean-room)
end note

note right of billedr
  **Trust Boundary**
  Signed entitlements issued
  by external authority.
end note

@enduml
